<article>
	<articleinfo>
		<title>Feature planning</title>
	</articleinfo>
	<section>
		<title>(fma) Features for release 0.1</title>
		<para>
			0.1 is scheduled for July 1st, 2013.
		</para>
		<para>
			We are aiming for the following features to be included in
			Eduras 0.1:
		</para>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					Player-centered scrolling
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					(Scaling and) full-screen mode.
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					At least three different weapons.
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					At least one seriously elaborate map.
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					Cooldown for weapons.
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					Make items be able to respawn.
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					An easily configurable server including features like
					server-restart,
					-shut and -open, gamemode- and map-change and
					limitations on
					playercount.
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					A more complete HUD showing healthpoints, weapons and
					eventually
					score correctly.
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					A very simple website where you can download Eduras from and
					which
					gives basic information about the game and its current and
					future
					features.
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					<emphasis role="strike">Support for EdurasViewer for Android and
						iOS.
					</emphasis>
				</para>
			</listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
	</section>
	<section>
	    <title>(fma) Features for release 0.1.1 (closed alpha)</title>
	    <itemizedlist>
	        <listitem>
	            <para>
	                 A launcher or something similar that keeps the user's game up-to-date
	            </para>
	        </listitem>
	        <listitem>
	            <para>
	                A meta server that keeps track of all registered Eduras servers, so users
	                can find online servers easily
	            </para>
	        </listitem>
	        <listitem>
	            <para>
	                A public bugtracker on the Eduras website
	            </para>
	        </listitem>
	    </itemizedlist>
	</section>
	<section>
		<title>(fma) Features for release 0.2</title>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					Dynamic objects (add/send them at runtime)
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					(limited) Ammunition for weapons
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>
					Smooth camera
				</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
				<para>Team deathmatch</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
			    <para>"Build mode", strategy elements, <emphasis>controlling units</emphasis>.</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
			    <para>Animation (Death, Loot,...)</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
			    <para>Elaborate Docbook (How to create
			        gameobjects, shapes, items, etc.)</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
			    <para>Access serverconsole from external (via client with role ADMIN and password)</para>
			</listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
	</section>
	<section>
		<title>Features for release 0.3</title>
		<itemizedlist>
			<listitem>
				<para>Capture-the-flag game mode</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
			    <para>Support for EdurasViewer for Android and iOS</para>
			</listitem>
			<listitem>
			    <para>Sound</para>
			</listitem>
		</itemizedlist>
	</section>
</article>